<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mersenne.inc | The Next Era of Intelligence</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS Variables for a futuristic dark theme */
        :root {
            --bg-color: #050814;
            --surface-color: #0f172a;
            --primary-color: #00f0ff; /* Neon Cyan */
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --font-main: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Reset & Base Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.7;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        nav {
            background-color: rgba(5, 8, 20, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .logo-placeholder {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        /* You can replace this div with an <img> tag when you sketch your logo */
        .logo-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), #0055ff);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        /* Hero Header */
        header {
            padding: 12rem 5% 8rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #0f172a 0%, #050814 100%);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, var(--primary-color));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
        }

        /* Main Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 5%;
        }

        /* Section Headers */
        h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        h2 span {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Products Section (CSS Grid) */
        .product-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .product-card {
            background-color: var(--surface-color);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .product-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .product-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .product-feature-list {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .product-feature-list li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .product-feature-list li::before {
            content: '▹';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        /* Vertical Timeline Section */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .timeline::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 2px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -1px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            padding: 10px 40px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: inherit;
            width: 50%;
        }

        .timeline-item::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            right: -8px;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            top: 15px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .left { left: 0; }
        .right { left: 50%; }
        .right::after { left: -8px; }

        .timeline-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: var(--surface-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .timeline-date {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: block;
        }

        /* Future Section */
        .future-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--surface-color) 0%, #081021 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .future-box p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--surface-color);
            padding: 3rem 5%;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        footer p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .timeline::after { left: 31px; }
            .timeline-item { width: 100%; padding-left: 70px; padding-right: 25px; }
            .timeline-item::after { left: 23px; }
            .right { left: 0%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo-placeholder">
            <div class="logo-icon"></div> Mersenne.inc
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#products">Products</a></li>
            <li><a href="#timeline">Timeline</a></li>
            <li><a href="#future">The Future</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header>
        <h1>Architecting Tomorrow.</h1>
        <p>Mersenne.inc is pioneering the next frontier of Artificial Intelligence, building intelligent software ecosystems and wearable hardware that reshape how humanity interacts with technology.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container" id="about">
        <h2>About <span>Us</span></h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p>At Mersenne.inc, we do not just write code; we build the future. Founded on the principle that machine learning should be both limitlessly powerful and deeply intuitive, we are developing a global enterprise focused on long-term technological breakthroughs.</p>
                <p>From complex neural networks to seamless daily-use hardware, our mission is to scale cutting-edge concepts into products that define the next generation of human capability.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--surface-color); border: 1px dashed rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 300px; color: var(--text-muted);">
                [ Conceptual AI Visualization Space ]
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" id="products">
        <h2>Our Core <span>Ecosystem</span></h2>
        <div class="product-grid">
            
            <div class="product-card">
                <h3>Glet</h3>
                <p>Our proprietary AI software architecture. Glet serves as the highly capable brain behind the Mersenne ecosystem, designed to process complex logic, learn from user interactions, and automate tasks at an unprecedented scale.</p>
                <ul class="product-feature-list">
                    <li>Advanced Machine Learning Algorithms</li>
                    <li>Natural Language Processing capabilities</li>
                    <li>Secure, scalable cloud integration</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="product-card">
                <h3>Edih</h3>
                <p>The bridge between artificial intelligence and visual reality. Edih smart glasses are lightweight, augmented-reality wearables that project Glet's intelligence directly into your field of view.</p>
                <ul class="product-feature-list">
                    <li>Hands-free augmented reality heads-up display</li>
                    <li>Real-time environmental analysis</li>
                    <li>Sleek, ergonomic design for all-day wear</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" id="timeline">
        <h2>The <span>Masterplan</span></h2>
        <div class="timeline">
            
            <div class="timeline-item left">
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <span class="timeline-date">Phase 1: Foundation & Research</span>
                    <p>Establishment of Mersenne.inc. Core focus on algorithm development, coding fundamentals, and conceptualizing the architecture for the Glet AI model.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item right">
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <span class="timeline-date">Phase 2: Glet Alpha</span>
                    <p>Development and internal testing of the first iteration of Glet. Refining the machine learning capabilities and ensuring stable processing power.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item left">
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <span class="timeline-date">Phase 3: Hardware Prototyping</span>
                    <p>Transitioning from software to physical integration. Designing the first wireframes and optical prototypes for the Edih smart glasses.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item right">
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <span class="timeline-date">Phase 4: Global Enterprise Market Launch</span>
                    <p>Unifying Glet and Edih into a seamless user experience. Launching the ecosystem globally and scaling Mersenne.inc operations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" id="future">
        <h2>The <span>Horizon</span></h2>
        <div class="future-box">
            <p>Our vision spans decades. We are not building products just for today; we are laying the groundwork for a multibillion-dollar global enterprise. By continuously pushing the boundaries of AI processing, robotics, and augmented reality, Mersenne.inc aims to become the undisputed global leader in the technology sector, driving human progress forward.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Mersenne.inc. Developed for the future.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
